"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Spinning as the process of making thread</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:19\">PRO 31:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28\">MAT 6:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:27\">LUK 12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Weaving as the process of making cloth</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a></p>\n<h2>Weavers and spinners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:9\">ISA 19:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:35\">EXO 35:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:22\">EXO 39:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27\">EXO 39:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:7\">2KI 23:7</a></p>\n<h2>The figurative use of spinning and weaving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6\">JOB 7:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:12\">ISA 38:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:13\">JDG 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:5\">ISA 59:5</a></p>",
